    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-10-22T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-10-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="329"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d329">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72119/2493</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">British Embassy</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Department of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right"> [<date
                            ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content" calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1918-10-22">October 22, 1918</date>,] [<hi rend="italic">Received
                            October 23, 1918.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">copy of telegram from mr. <persName corresp="#p_BAJ1"
                            >balfour</persName> to mr. <persName corresp="#p_BC1">barclay</persName>
                        october 22, 1918</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The British Government have been approached by the Turkish Government and have
                    authorised the British Naval Commander-in-Chief at Mudros to discuss armistice
                    with accredited Turkish representatives.</p>
                <p>We have told our Admiral to obtain, if possible, all the conditions suggested at
                    Versailles, but in our judgment the immediate complete opening of the
                    Dardanelles and Bosphorus and secure access to the Black Sea are of such
                    paramount importance and so obviously carry everything else with them that if he
                    can obtain these he may accept armistice at once.</p>
                <p>Please inform the Government to which you are accredited.</p>
                <closer>[No signature indicated]</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
